snippet.title: The Divine Speaker Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's a look at our brand new trailer for the BL Visual Novel, The Divine Speaker.

Play the demo:
Itch -  https://gabmag.itch.io/the-divine-speaker
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1373950/The_Divine_Speaker/

Follow us on Twitter for updates: https://twitter.com/thedvspgame

Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/twoandahalfstudios

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/xGPGXra

KotoriMWorks: Video Editing
Fuyuure: Character Art
